started eliminating

00:53:35.200 --> 00:53:39.680 align:middle line:84%
the budgets for poetry,
for art, for expression,

00:53:39.680 --> 00:53:42.260 align:middle line:90%
arts in public education.

00:53:42.260 --> 00:53:44.680 align:middle line:84%
And this is something
that preceded it.

00:53:44.680 --> 00:53:46.304 align:middle line:90%
And this is a beautiful quote.

