00:54:26.320 --> 00:54:27.588 align:middle line:90%
is share this kind of stuff.

00:54:27.588 --> 00:54:28.088 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:54:28.088 --> 00:54:30.660 align:middle line:10%
John F. Kennedy.

00:54:30.660 --> 00:54:33.640 align:middle line:84%
"When power leads
men toward arrogance,

00:54:33.640 --> 00:54:37.470 align:middle line:84%
poetry reminds him
of his limitations.

00:54:37.470 --> 00:54:40.090 align:middle line:10%
When power narrows the
areas of man's concern,

00:54:40.090 --> 00:54:43.200 align:middle line:10%
poetry reminds him of the
richness and diversity

00:54:43.200 --> 00:54:44.840 align:middle line:10%
of his existence.

00:54:44.840 --> 00:54:48.340 align:middle line:10%
When power corrupts,
poetry cleanses.

00:54:48.340 --> 00:54:51.930 align:middle line:84%
For art establishes
the basic human truth

00:54:51.930 --> 00:54:56.360 align:middle line:84%
which must serve as the
touchstone of our judgment.

00:54:56.360 --> 00:55:00.680 align:middle line:10%
The artist, however faithful to
his personal vision of reality,

00:55:00.680 --> 00:55:05.890 align:middle line:10%
becomes the last champion of the
individual mind and sensibility

00:55:05.890 --> 00:55:09.530 align:middle line:10%
against an intrusive society
and an officious state."

